    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The undersurfaces of shoes, boots, or other footwear that make contact with the ground; the parts upon which the wearer treads. These are usually made from firm but flexible materials such as rubber or leather.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
